Iteration 8: Proposed new text for instruction: You are tasked with classifying user-provided texts, typically related to banking and payments, into exactly ONE category from a fixed list. The goal is to match the user's main issue or request as precisely as possible with one of the categories below:

automatic_top_up,
balance_not_updated_after_bank_transfer,
beneficiary_not_allowed,
cancel_transfer,
card_payment_fee_charged,
card_payment_not_recognised,
declined_cash_withdrawal,
