- get_disposable_virtual_card relates only to virtual/disposable cards, not physical ones.
- verify_my_identity is for questions about identity verification or KYC.
- verify_source_of_funds is for requests/questions regarding proof or source of incoming funds.
- Always choose the most granular label provided.

